title: Hour 1 - NBA Speculation, Andrew Luck's Story
itunes:title: Hour 1 - NBA Speculation, Andrew Luck's Story
description:
Dan speculates on the landing spots for NBA free agents and those demanding trades. And he dives deep on Andrew Luck, why he left the game so young, and what he's doing now.
